p_table <- function(tab_data, ...) {
  tab_data_2 <- deparse(substitute(tab_data))
  
  table_p <- do.call(CreateTableOne, 
                     list(data = as.name(tab_data_2), includeNA = TRUE, ...))
  table_p_out <- print(table_p,
                       showAllLevels = TRUE,
                       printToggle = FALSE)
  kable(table_p_out,
        align = "c")
}

  yearAbx[i,2] <- nrow(data %>% filter(abxUsed & YEAR == year)) / 
            nrow(data %>% filter(YEAR == year))
  print(c(year, "-", 
          nrow(data %>% filter(abxUsed & YEAR == year)) / 
            nrow(data %>% filter(YEAR == year))))
  i <- i +1
}

withSpecs <- data %>% filter(!is.na(Specialties))

specAbx <- matrix(nrow = 14, ncol = 2)
specAbx[,1] <- levels(withSpecs$Specialties)

i <- 1
for(spec in specAbx[,1]) {
  specAbx[i,2] <- as.numeric(nrow(withSpecs %>% filter(abxUsed & Specialties == spec)) / 
            nrow(withSpecs %>% filter(Specialties == spec)))
  
  print(c(spec, "-", 
          nrow(withSpecs %>% filter(abxUsed & Specialties == spec)) / 
            nrow(withSpecs %>% filter(Specialties == spec))))
  i <- i +1
}
